Installation Instructions
-------------------------

1. Deploy subversive.war on a J2EE server.

2. Copy subversive.conf.dist to either /etc/subversive.conf or to the home directory
   of the user running the J2EE server as .subversive.conf.

3. Edit the configuration file to taste. Reloading of the application is not
   necessary!

-------------------------

See also:
    http://code.google.com/p/subversive-manager/wiki/InstallationInstructions
